item.title: ICSWP get along swimmingly at their annual team gala in Cambridge
item.author: Clara Bachorz,David Moores,
item.description: The first swimming gala of the year saw ICSWP go to Cambridge for their annual team gala. Sporting their finest navy and red new kit, a team of 18 Imperial swimmers arrived ready to impress, competed like champions, and left with their heads held high.
